author: chirino
msg: Added a new index to order messages by a sequence id instead of a the Location.
The problem was that messages in a transaction have a location id the comes earlier
than messages not in a transaction, but those transacted messages should be recovered

author: dkulp
msg: * Fixed build failure in mtom sample. resource file was being copied to wrong location.
* Modified build.xml to replace hardcoded SERVICEMIX_VERSION in jar file name to use wildcard for ease of moving between versions
Change the default to not throw an exception when encountering an unknown extensor.  Parse it into a XmlPrimitiveAssertion and allow the effective policy computation consider other alternatives.
When not using 'soap encoding', map Character objects to xsd:strings.
[CXF-1334] Remove the now un-used eclipse stuff
[CXF-1779]exclude Map or Collection property as well which entry may not be serializable
Update policy engine to parse policies in any namespace.   No need to configure a namespace now.
Fix checkstyle error and build failure

author: jsdelfino
msg: Added a little more logic to restart the domain manager or a node when the user presses 'r', quit when the user presses 'q'.

author: jsdelfino
msg: Removed leftover calls to System.out.println polluting the output.

msg: Restart a node when the user just presses enter.
